errors.name: PriceTooHigh
errors.msg: Buy price was higher than the maximum buy price. Try increasing max_price or slippage configuration

errors.name: PriceTooLow
errors.msg: Sell price was lower than the minimum sell price. Try decreasing min_price or increasing slippage configuration

errors.name: MintSupplyTooLow
errors.msg: Cannot sell more than the target mint currently has in supply

errors.name: SellDisabled
errors.msg: Sell is not enabled on this bonding curve

errors.name: NotLiveYet

errors.name: OverPurchaseCap
errors.msg: Cannot purchase that many tokens because of purchase cap

errors.name: BuyFrozen
errors.msg: Buy is frozen on this bonding curve, purchases not allowed

errors.name: WrappedSolNotAllowed
errors.msg: Use token bonding wrapped sol via buy_wrapped_sol, sell_wrapped_sol commands. We may one day provide liquid staking rewards on this stored sol.

errors.name: InvalidMint
errors.msg: An account was provided that did not have the correct mint

errors.name: IgnoreExternalV1Only
errors.msg: Ignoring external changes is only supported on v1 of buy and sell endpoints. Please upgrade your client

errors.name: InvalidPad
errors.msg: Cannot pad token bonding without ignoring external reserve and supply changes. This is an advanced feature, incorrect use could lead to insufficient resreves to cover sells
